    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8018-9257-cd7d14c47e3c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Evaluates how different attributes affect collaborative learning in the context of computer education. Authors conduct a set of experiments with table size, group size and gender and measure their effects on a sample of university students.,",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
